Third-party files vendored under external/reshade-sdk/
======================================================

The files in this directory are unmodified, byte-for-byte copies of
sources from two upstream open source projects.  Each file retains its
original copyright header (and SPDX-License-Identifier where present).
This document collects the license texts so that recipients of source
and binary distributions of the parent project (CrimsonDesertLiveTransmog)
receive the notices required by the upstream licenses.


Components
----------

1. Dear ImGui (subset)
   Files:    include/imgui.h, include/imconfig.h
   Upstream: https://github.com/ocornut/imgui
   Copyright (C) 2014-2026 Omar Cornut
   License:  MIT

2. ReShade SDK headers
   Files:    include/reshade.hpp
             include/reshade_api.hpp
             include/reshade_api_device.hpp
             include/reshade_api_format.hpp
             include/reshade_api_pipeline.hpp
             include/reshade_api_resource.hpp
             include/reshade_events.hpp
             include/reshade_overlay.hpp
   Upstream: https://github.com/crosire/reshade
   Copyright (C) 2021 Patrick Mours
   SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause OR MIT

3. ReShade host-side imgui function-table populator
   Files:    source/imgui_function_table_19250.hpp
             source/imgui_function_table_19250.cpp
   Upstream: https://github.com/crosire/reshade
   Copyright (C) 2021 Patrick Mours
   Copyright (C) 2014-2026 Omar Cornut
   SPDX-License-Identifier: BSD-3-Clause OR MIT

Components (2) and (3) are dual-licensed under BSD-3-Clause OR MIT.
The recipient may choose either license.  Both license texts are
reproduced below to satisfy the source- and binary-distribution
notice requirements of whichever the recipient selects.


